'''''Cloak & Dagger''''' is an [[arcade video game]] released by [[Atari, Inc.]] in March 1984 as a tie-in to the 1984 film ''[[Cloak & Dagger (1984 film)|Cloak & Dagger]]''. The game saw limited arcade release as a conversion kit for ''[[Robotron: 2084]]'' cabinets.

